1. what are signals
2  Types of signals	
	- General purpose
	- real time 
3. How Applications can handle an signal event
	- Default handler
	- custom handler
	- ignore
4. establishing signal handler 
	- using signal() api
	- using sigaction() api
5. sigaction flags
	-SA_RESTART
	-SA_NODEFER
	-SA_RESETHAND
	-SA_ONSTACK
	-SA_NOCLDSTOP
	-SA_NOCLDWAIT
6. Blocking signal Delivery
	- During exectuion of a priority signal handler
		-sigaction with sa_mask field
	- During execution of critical operation in main thread
		- sigprocmask() api
